import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react'
import './restaurants.css'
function Restaurants() {
 
 const [restaurants,setRestaurants]=useState(
 [{
    name: "Mothers's Kitchen",
    deliveryTime: 30,
    relevance: 4,
    rating: 4,
    cost:200,
    description:'North Indian, South Indian',
    image:"https://images.pexels.com/photos/1640772/pexels-photo-1640772.jpeg?cs=srgb&dl=pexels-ella-olsson-1640772.jpg&fm=jpg"
  },
  {
    name: 'Zam Zam Hotel',
    deliveryTime: 25,
    relevance: 5,
    rating: 4.5,
    cost:150,
    description:'Chinese, North indian,South Indian',
    image:'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcR7ZQweZXJuwPizDP_oV1Qg27jrme9FQ9IXBw&usqp=CAUg'
  },
  {
    name: 'The Imperial Kitchen',
    deliveryTime: 35,
    relevance: 4.7,
    rating: 4.2,
    cost:500,
    description:'Chinese, North indian,South Indian',
    image:'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcS5dAG2vG0JeLl3OyKe6zEolYkZ-J42xFka7Q&usqp=CAU'
  },
  {
    name: 'Al Baik Feasto Express',
    deliveryTime: 40,
    relevance: 5,
    rating: 5,
    cost:400,
    description:'Chinese, North indian,South Indian',
    image:'data:image/jpeg;base64,'
  },
  {
    name: 'Malabar Kitchen',
    deliveryTime: 38,
    relevance: 4.9,
    rating: 4.5,
    cost:200,
    description:'Chinese, North indian,South Indian',
    image:'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRAVlCf-w-_qejk3uh_42d-FW1TIPGxOPV95Q&usqp=CAU'
  },
])


const filterRestaurants=(value)=>{
    if (value==='Rating') {
      
      const sortedRestaurantsList = [...restaurants].sort((a, b) => b.rating - a.rating);
        setRestaurants(sortedRestaurantsList)
        console.log(...restaurants);
        console.log(sortedRestaurantsList);
    }
    else if (value==='Delivery Time') {
      const sortedRestaurantsList = [...restaurants].sort((a, b) => a.deliveryTime - b.deliveryTime);
      setRestaurants(sortedRestaurantsList)
      console.log(...restaurants);
      console.log(sortedRestaurantsList);
    }
    else if (value==='Cost: Low To High') {
      const sortedRestaurantsList = [...restaurants].sort((a, b) => a.cost - b.cost);
      setRestaurants(sortedRestaurantsList)
      console.log(...restaurants);
      console.log(sortedRestaurantsList);
    }
    else if (value==='Relevance') {
      const sortedRestaurantsList = [...restaurants].sort((a, b) => a.relevance - b.relevance);
      setRestaurants(sortedRestaurantsList)
      console.log(...restaurants);
      console.log(sortedRestaurantsList);
    }
    else{
      const sortedRestaurantsList = [...restaurants].sort((a, b) => b.cost - a.cost);
      setRestaurants(sortedRestaurantsList)
      console.log(...restaurants);
      console.log(sortedRestaurantsList);
    }
}
  return (
    <div className='container'>
      <div className='filters'>
       <h1>373 restaurants</h1>
        <div className='filter-options'>
           <button onClick={(e)=>{
             const filterValue=e.target.textContent
              console.log(filterValue);
              filterRestaurants(filterValue)
           }}>Relevance</button>
           <button  onClick={(e)=>{
             const filterValue=e.target.textContent
              console.log(filterValue);
              filterRestaurants(filterValue)
           }}>Delivery Time</button>
           <button  onClick={(e)=>{
             const filterValue=e.target.textContent
              console.log(filterValue);
              filterRestaurants(filterValue)
           }}>Rating</button>
           <button  onClick={(e)=>{
             const filterValue=e.target.textContent
              console.log(filterValue);
              filterRestaurants(filterValue)
           }}>Cost: Low To High</button> 
           <button  onClick={(e)=>{
             const filterValue=e.target.textContent
              console.log(filterValue);
              filterRestaurants(filterValue)
           }}>Cost: High To Low</button>
           <button id='filter-icon'><span>Filters</span> <i class="fa-solid fa-sliders fa-rotate-90"></i></button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div className='restaurants'>

        {restaurants.map((restautent=>{
          return(

            <div className="restaurant-details">
          
          <img src={restautent.image} alt="" />
          <h3>{restautent.name}</h3>
          <p>{restautent.description}</p>
          <div className='restaurant-review'>
            <div id='rate'>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
            <span>{restautent.rating}</span>
            </div>
            <span>{restautent.deliveryTime} minutes</span>
            <span id='currency'><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="48" viewBox="0 96 960 960" width="48"><path d="M564 936 290 652v-66h130q57 0 100-37t50-103H240v-60h325q-13-48-53.5-79T420 276H240v-60h480v60H566q23 20 39 51t23 59h92v60h-90q-8 91-67.5 145.5T420 646h-52l279 290h-83Z"/></svg>{restautent.cost} fOR TWO</span>
          </div>
            <hr />
            <button>QUICK VIEW</button>
        </div>
        )
        }))}


       
      </div>
    </div>
  )
}

export default Restaurants
